                Made with <a href="https://symfony.com/" target="_blank">Symfony</a> &
                <a href="https://bulma.io" target="_blank">Bulma</a><br>
                Hosting: <a href="https://www.clever-cloud.com" target="_blank">Clever Cloud</a>
